rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0001
rows.name: So, what should I whip up today?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11010100_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask for the Chef Koo Choice.

rows.label: xs11010100_SEL0013
rows.name: Ask for the Lin Lee Special.

rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0003
rows.name: We need you in the hangar—now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0005
rows.name: It's Lao, he— Hey! Get away from that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0005_2
rows.name: Elma, get yer butts over here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0006
rows.name:
What was that all about?
Did I hear him talking to Lao?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11010100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Whatever it was, it didn't sound very good.
We'd better get to the hangar ASAP.[ST:wait ]
